04:55.462 --> 04:56.255
ALL NOW, RIGHT?

04:56.379 --> 04:57.756
>> DID THE MAYOR GIVE MY DADDY

04:57.881 --> 04:58.548
HIS JOB BACK?

04:58.673 --> 04:59.424
>> SORRY, GUYS.

