IT AS ALL THE OTHER --

05:05.847 --> 05:07.224
>> THERE IS NOTHING LINKING

05:07.348 --> 05:08.934
DR. MOROCCO TO THE MODULE, CODY,

05:09.059 --> 05:10.685
OR TO ANYTHING ELSE YOU'VE FOUND

05:10.811 --> 05:11.937
WITH THAT SAME EMBLEM.

05:12.062 --> 05:12.896
I'M SORRY.

05:13.021 --> 05:14.481
