>> AH, FRANKIE, THERE YOU ARE.

05:19.611 --> 05:21.238
>> DOC, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

05:21.362 --> 05:23.115
>> WELL, OLD FRIEND, I'M SORRY

05:23.240 --> 05:24.658
TO SAY, I'M PACKING UP.

