>> NO!

05:35.210 --> 05:36.837
>> BUT WE CAN'T LEAVE

05:36.962 --> 05:38.046
GRIFFIN ROCK.

05:38.172 --> 05:40.423
>> UNLESS I CAN GET MY OLD JOB

05:40.548 --> 05:42.801
BACK, WHICH SEEMS UNLIKELY, WE

05:42.926 --> 05:46.305
