>> AWW. THANKS, BLADES.

06:19.129 --> 06:20.339
DON'T WORRY, WE'LL BE IN THE AIR

06:20.463 --> 06:21.340
AGAIN SOON.

06:21.464 --> 06:23.258
>> WOULD  NOW  BE SOON ENOUGH?

06:23.382 --> 06:24.926
