11:04.164 --> 11:05.373
>> ARE YOU GONNA DO THAT ALL

11:05.499 --> 11:07.375
DAY?

11:07.501 --> 11:08.668
>> JUST STAYING SHARP.

11:08.793 --> 11:10.253
NEVER KNOW WHAT OPTIMUS MIGHT

11:10.378 --> 11:11.421
HAVE IN MIND FOR US.

11:11.546 --> 11:13.173
>> SO YOU'D HAVE NO PROBLEM JUST

11:13.298 --> 11:14.257
