11:14.382 --> 11:15.425
>> I'M A RESCUE BOT.

11:15.550 --> 11:16.759
IT'S ALL I KNOW.

11:16.884 --> 11:18.428
MAYBE HERE, IN GRIFFIN ROCK, I'M

11:18.553 --> 11:19.387
OUTDATED, BUT --

11:19.513 --> 11:21.055
>> NO, YOU'RE NOT.

11:21.181 --> 11:25.393
I MEAN...NONE OF US IS.

11:25.519 --> 11:27.395
[ SPLAT! ]

11:27.521 --> 11:28.896
>> WHAT IS IT?

11:29.022 --> 11:29.939
>> PEA SOUP.

11:30.064 --> 11:31.107
ACCORDING TO MY RESEARCH, THERE

11:31.232 --> 11:32.359
ARE MANY EXCITING CAREER

11:32.484 --> 11:33.860
OPPORTUNITIES FOR GOURMET CHEFS.

11:33.985 --> 11:35.278
BON APPéTIT.

11:40.033 --> 11:41.660
>> I HAD A BIG BREAKFAST.

11:41.784 --> 11:43.161
>> THEN, DO YOU MIND?

11:43.286 --> 11:44.454
I'M OUT OF GREEN.

11:44.579 --> 11:46.540
>> ALL YOURS.

11:51.419 --> 11:53.630
SO THIS MEANS YOU'RE FEELING...

11:53.754 --> 11:55.965
>> NOT SO ROSY.

11:56.090 --> 11:57.467
KIND OF EXPECTED TO BE BACK ON

11:57.592 --> 11:58.968
THE JOB BY NOW.

11:59.093 --> 12:00.053
>> ME TOO, BUDDY.

12:00.178 --> 12:01.804
BUT LET'S STAY POSITIVE, HUH?

12:01.929 --> 12:03.515
AND HOWEVER THIS TURNS OUT...

12:03.640 --> 12:05.392
we absolutely must keep Chase

12:05.517 --> 12:06.685
out of the kitchen.

12:06.809 --> 12:09.896
>> SO GLAD I DON'T EAT.

12:17.612 --> 12:18.863
>> DID YOU BRING YOUR DAD'S

12:18.988 --> 12:19.614
FLASH DRIVE?

12:19.738 --> 12:20.532
>> 100 TERABYTES.

12:20.657 --> 12:21.908
BIG ENOUGH TO HOLD WHATEVER

12:22.033 --> 12:23.034
COMPUTER FILES YOU SAW

12:23.159 --> 12:27.038
DR. MOROCCO WORKING ON.

12:27.163 --> 12:28.498
>> HOW ARE WE GOING TO GET IN?

12:28.623 --> 12:29.708
>> I USED TO LIVE HERE,

12:29.832 --> 12:31.376
REMEMBER?

12:31.501 --> 12:33.086
HOLOGRAPHIC DOGGIE DOOR --

12:33.211 --> 12:34.837
INVISIBLE TO PEOPLE, NOT TO

12:34.962 --> 12:36.673
DOGS.

12:36.797 --> 12:41.678
>> I totally want one of these.

12:41.802 --> 12:44.347
[ FOOTSTEPS ]

12:44.472 --> 12:47.308
>> I ASSURE YOU, MANY DEVICES IN

12:47.434 --> 12:50.144
MY INVENTORY CAN BE WEAPONIZED.

12:50.270 --> 12:51.479
SOUNDS AS IF YOU'RE BUILDING AN

12:51.605 --> 12:54.190
ARMY.

12:54.315 --> 12:56.526
YOU ARE?

12:56.651 --> 12:58.528
THEN LET'S DISCUSS MY BULK

12:58.653 --> 12:59.738
RATES.

13:03.533 --> 13:04.867
>> HE'S SELLING ALL OF

13:04.992 --> 13:06.160
GRIFFIN ROCK'S TECH.

13:06.286 --> 13:07.370
>> THERE'LL BE NOTHING LEFT ON

13:07.495 --> 13:07.912
THE ISLAND.

13:08.037 --> 13:09.664
LET'S GO.

13:19.633 --> 13:22.510
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

13:22.636 --> 13:25.179
[ BEEP ]

13:25.305 --> 13:27.848
>> MY PASSWORD'S NOT WORKING.

13:27.974 --> 13:29.350
HE MUST HAVE CHANGED IT.

13:29.476 --> 13:29.976
>> YES.

13:30.101 --> 13:30.893
[ BOTH GASP ]

13:31.018 --> 13:34.230
HE MUST HAVE.

13:34.355 --> 13:39.319
CLEVER MAN, THAT DR. MOROCCO.

13:45.742 --> 13:48.453
>> OH, GOODY.

13:48.578 --> 13:50.121
A GAME.

13:50.246 --> 13:53.958
MORBOT -- SEEK.

13:54.083 --> 13:58.797
[ THUDDING ]

13:58.921 --> 14:00.881
[ BEEPING ]

14:06.638 --> 14:08.264
>> WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS TO

14:08.389 --> 14:09.223
GRIFFIN ROCK?

14:09.349 --> 14:11.184
>> WHAT DID MY FATHER EVER DO TO

14:11.309 --> 14:14.228
YOU?

14:14.354 --> 14:16.897
>> DO YOU KNOW HOW HARD IT IS TO

14:17.023 --> 14:19.275
RESTORE A DAMAGED REPUTATION?

14:19.400 --> 14:21.778
WELL, DOC GREENE WILL FIND OUT.

14:21.902 --> 14:24.113
JUST AS I DID WHEN I WAS SHUT

14:24.238 --> 14:26.157
OUT OF THIS JOB YEARS AGO.

14:26.282 --> 14:28.618
WORD SPREAD THAT IT WAS BECAUSE

14:28.743 --> 14:31.954
MY TECHNOLOGY WAS INFERIOR.

14:32.079 --> 14:33.790
>> THAT'S BECAUSE IT IS.

14:33.914 --> 14:35.958
>> SAYS WHOM?

14:36.083 --> 14:37.960
OH, AHA! I KNOW.

14:38.085 --> 14:40.630
DOC GREENE, THE MAYOR,

14:40.755 --> 14:42.799
CHIEF BURNS.

14:42.923 --> 14:45.968
THEY MADE ME A PARIAH.

14:46.093 --> 14:48.471
I'M MAKING THEM...

14:48.596 --> 14:51.641
OBSOLETE.

14:51.766 --> 14:54.811
>> OVER THERE!

14:54.935 --> 14:56.646
>> [ GRUNTS ]

14:56.771 --> 15:00.316
DISPOSE OF THEM!

15:00.441 --> 15:00.983
>> [ PANTING ]

15:01.108 --> 15:02.485
THIS WAY!

15:02.610 --> 15:03.903
[ BOTH PANTING ]

15:07.824 --> 15:11.118
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

15:15.540 --> 15:17.458
>> [ PANTING ] WE'RE TRAPPED!

15:22.380 --> 15:24.424
[ BEEPING ]

15:24.549 --> 15:26.760
>> WELL, THAT'S UNFORTUNATE.

15:26.885 --> 15:28.428
[ RAPID BEEPING ]

15:28.553 --> 15:31.931
[ EXPLOSION ]

15:32.056 --> 15:34.100
[ BEEP ]

15:34.225 --> 15:35.268
[ TELEPHONES RINGING ]

15:35.393 --> 15:36.561
>> [ GASPS ]

15:36.686 --> 15:38.688
WHAT IS GOING ON HERE?

15:38.813 --> 15:39.564
>> HOLD, PLEASE.

15:39.689 --> 15:40.899
MORE COMPLAINTS ABOUT THE

15:41.023 --> 15:42.066
MORBOT, MAYOR.

15:42.191 --> 15:43.651
"IT PUT A HOLE IN MY ROOF."

15:43.777 --> 15:45.403
"IT DESTROYED THE PLAYGROUND."

15:45.528 --> 15:47.071
"REMEMBER THIS WHEN YOU'RE UP

15:47.196 --> 15:48.155
FOR RE-ELECTION!"

15:48.281 --> 15:49.824
ASSEMBLE THE COUNCIL AT ONCE!

15:49.949 --> 15:50.658
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

15:50.784 --> 15:52.285
>> MAYOR'S OFFICE. WHAT?

15:52.410 --> 15:54.245
THERE'S A FIRE UP AT THE LAB!

15:54.370 --> 15:56.163
DR. MOROCCO ISN'T RESPONDING!

15:56.289 --> 15:58.499
>> UM...CALL THE CHIEF.

15:58.625 --> 16:00.000
[ ALARM WAILS ]

16:00.126 --> 16:01.502
[ BEEPING ]

16:01.628 --> 16:04.839
[ MACHINERY HUMMING ]

16:04.964 --> 16:07.675
[ FIRE POLE SQUEAKS ]

16:07.801 --> 16:09.009
>> WHAT'S GOING ON?

16:09.135 --> 16:10.470
>> WHO RANG THE ALARM?

16:10.595 --> 16:11.971
[ FOOTSTEPS ]

16:12.096 --> 16:12.972
>> I DID.

16:13.097 --> 16:14.641
THE GRIFFIN ROCK LAB'S ON FIRE.

16:14.766 --> 16:16.559
DR. MOROCCO MIGHT BE IN TROUBLE

16:16.684 --> 16:17.477
UP THERE.

16:17.602 --> 16:18.812
>> SO, WHY ISN'T THE MORBOT

16:18.937 --> 16:19.687
HANDLING IT?

16:19.813 --> 16:21.063
>> NO IDEA, AND IT DOESN'T

16:21.188 --> 16:22.064
MATTER.

16:22.189 --> 16:23.650
THE REAL QUESTION IS, DO WE HELP

16:23.775 --> 16:25.693
PEOPLE OR NOT?

16:35.703 --> 16:37.079
>> RESCUE BOTS -- ROLL TO THE

16:37.204 --> 16:38.247
RESCUE!

16:38.372 --> 16:44.128
[ SIRENS WAIL ]

16:44.253 --> 16:46.297
[ FIRE SMOLDERING ]

16:46.422 --> 16:52.470
[ CRASH! ]

16:52.595 --> 16:55.640
[ BEEPING ]

16:55.765 --> 16:56.307
>> [ GASPS ]

16:56.432 --> 16:57.851
IN THERE!

17:06.108 --> 17:07.819
[ BEEPING ]

17:07.944 --> 17:09.487
[ MECHANICAL DOORS CLOSE ]

17:09.612 --> 17:10.655
[ ALARM WAILING ]

17:10.780 --> 17:12.824
>> HANG ON!

17:12.949 --> 17:17.996
[ PROPELLERS WHIRL ]

17:18.120 --> 17:22.834
[ BOTH PANTING ]

17:22.959 --> 17:25.211
[ GASPS ]

17:25.336 --> 17:26.212
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

17:26.337 --> 17:28.882
[ METAL CLANGING ]

17:29.007 --> 17:31.384
>> [ GASPS ]

17:31.509 --> 17:32.719
>> [ GASPS ]

17:32.844 --> 17:35.346
UH...CODY, YOU MIGHT WANT TO

17:35.471 --> 17:37.056
TAKE A LOOK AT THIS.

17:42.645 --> 17:43.521
BUSTED.

17:43.646 --> 17:45.356
>> YOU DOWNLOAD.

17:45.481 --> 17:47.191
I'LL RADIO FOR HELP.

17:50.653 --> 17:53.614
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRL ]

18:00.538 --> 18:02.790
>> Dani! Can you hear me?

18:02.916 --> 18:05.084
>> CODY, WHERE ARE YOU?

18:05.209 --> 18:06.168
>> Frankie and I are in the

18:06.293 --> 18:07.378
blimp, and the Morbot's chasing

18:07.503 --> 18:08.337
us.

18:08.462 --> 18:08.796
I don't know how to land this

18:08.922 --> 18:10.048
thing.

18:16.763 --> 18:18.138
>> ANY SIGN OF DR. MOROCCO?

18:18.264 --> 18:19.724
>> NO, MUST HAVE TAKEN OFF IN

18:19.849 --> 18:20.516
HIS AIRSHIP.

18:20.641 --> 18:25.229
[ PROPELLERS WHIRL ]

18:25.354 --> 18:27.273
>> AND IT LOOKS LIKE HE'S COMING

18:27.398 --> 18:27.732
BACK.

18:27.857 --> 18:28.649
PERFECT.

18:28.775 --> 18:31.277
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRL ]

18:31.402 --> 18:32.862
>> THAT'S NOT DR. MOROCCO.

18:32.987 --> 18:34.447
THAT'S CODY AND FRANKIE...

18:34.572 --> 18:36.699
AND THE MORBOT!

18:41.788 --> 18:46.667
>> IT'S BREAKING DOWN THE DOOR!

18:46.793 --> 18:47.752
>> NOW WHAT, DANI?

18:47.877 --> 18:49.378
>> I'm gonna bring you down in

18:49.503 --> 18:50.296
Town Square.

18:50.421 --> 18:51.714
You've seen me land Blades a

18:51.839 --> 18:52.590
hundred times.

18:52.715 --> 18:53.591
Same thing.

18:53.716 --> 18:56.260
Take the cyclic lever and push.

18:56.385 --> 19:00.431
The nose will go down.

19:00.556 --> 19:02.266
>> IT'S WORKING. NOW WHAT?

19:02.391 --> 19:04.226
>> Twist the throttle back to

19:04.351 --> 19:05.269
reduce speed.

19:05.394 --> 19:06.604
[ THROTTLE CRANKS ]

19:06.729 --> 19:12.443
[ PROPELLERS WHIRL ]

19:12.568 --> 19:14.278
[ SIRENS WAIL ]

19:14.403 --> 19:18.282
[ BEEPING ]

19:18.407 --> 19:21.119
>> [ SCREAMS ]

19:21.243 --> 19:23.121
IT BROKE THROUGH!

19:23.245 --> 19:25.123
[ BEEPING ]

19:25.247 --> 19:27.291
>> HANG ON!

19:27.416 --> 19:28.459
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

19:28.584 --> 19:33.798
[ METAL SCREECHES ]

19:33.923 --> 19:34.882
[ BEEP ]

19:44.266 --> 19:45.726
[ SIRENS WAIL ]

19:54.110 --> 19:56.487
>> YOU ARE SAFE NOW.

19:56.612 --> 19:59.073
>> I LOVE THESE GUYS.

19:59.198 --> 20:04.912
[ BEEPING ]

20:05.038 --> 20:08.791
[ METAL CLANGING ]

20:10.960 --> 20:13.171
>> MORBOT DECOMMISSIONED.

20:13.295 --> 20:15.173
>> AND THE  LESS  MORBOT, THE

20:15.297 --> 20:17.175
BETTER.

20:17.299 --> 20:18.467
>> WHAT WERE YOU TWO DOING IN

20:18.592 --> 20:19.301
THAT THING?

20:19.426 --> 20:20.219
YOU COULD HAVE BEEN HURT.

20:20.344 --> 20:21.428
>> YOU SAID WE CAN'T ACCUSE

20:21.554 --> 20:23.597
DR. MOROCCO WITHOUT EVIDENCE.

20:23.723 --> 20:25.933
>> SO, WE GOT YOU SOME.

20:26.059 --> 20:31.480
ACTUALLY, LOTS.

20:31.605 --> 20:35.193
>> ALL IN FAVOR?

20:41.490 --> 20:47.038
[ ALL CHEER ]

20:47.163 --> 20:49.540
[ ALARMS BEEP, WAIL ]

20:49.665 --> 20:51.625
>> SOMETHING WRONG WITH YOUR

20:51.751 --> 20:53.460
RESCUE VEHICLES, CHIEF?

20:53.586 --> 20:55.213
>> NO, THEY'RE PERFECT.

20:55.337 --> 20:56.380
JUST, UH...UNLOCKING THE DOORS.

20:56.505 --> 20:58.049
[ ALARMS STOP ]

20:58.174 --> 20:59.341
COME ON, EVERYONE!

20:59.466 --> 21:00.843
BARBECUE AT OUR HOUSE.

21:00.968 --> 21:03.221
>> THE RESCUE BOTS, THE BURNSES,

21:03.345 --> 21:05.347
DOC GREENE -- ALL BACK WHERE

21:05.472 --> 21:06.432
THEY BELONG.

21:06.557 --> 21:08.684
ONCE AGAIN, THE STREETS OF OUR

21:08.809 --> 21:10.728
TOWN WILL BE PROTECTED WITH

21:10.853 --> 21:12.980
COMPASSION AND REASON, AS WELL

21:13.106 --> 21:14.440
AS WITH STRENGTH.

21:14.565 --> 21:17.235
AND, FOR TONIGHT, ALL IS WELL IN

21:17.359 --> 21:18.945
GRIFFIN ROCK.

21:20.571 --> 21:22.949
>> [ SCOFFS ]
